msgid ""
"**Hardware**: At least 4 GPUs (2 for prefillers + 2 for decoders in 2p2d "
"setup)"
msgstr "**硬件**：至少需要 4 个 GPU（2 个用于 Prefillers + 2 个用于 2p2d 设置中的解码器）"

