msgstr "**网络瓶颈**：监控实例之间的 NIXL 传输性能"

#: ../../source/disaggregated_prefill/nixl/xpyd.rst:353
msgid "**Startup Timing**: Stagger prefiller launches to avoid resource conflicts"
msgstr "**启动时机**：错开 Prefill 启动以避免资源冲突"

